      "span_text": "When researchers tested the OMOP common data model in the THIN database, they mapped medical and drug codes. Twenty-five percent of the diagnosis codes and 55 % of the drug codes in the raw THIN database were not retrieved with the OMOP terminology dictionary [CITATION_1] ."
